:</u></strong><br><br><br>• Hide and Sneak<br><br>• Puzzles and investigations are integrated into the game for variety of gameplay.<br><br>• Unpredictable Enemies<br><br>• Deadly combat and stealth<br><br>• Challenging Gameplay",
